"Basic settings"
set nocompatible "Fixes old Vi bugs
syntax on "Turns on syntax highlighting
set backspace=indent,eol,start "Makes backspace work
set history=200 "Sets undo history
set ruler "Sets up status bar
set number "Turns on line numbering
set tabstop=4 "Sets indent size
set shiftwidth=4 "See above
let &t_Co=256 "Sets terminal to use 256 colors
colorscheme elflord "Sets colorscheme to elflord

"Search settings
set hlsearch "Highlights search terms
set showmatch "Highlights matching parentheses
set ignorecase "Ignores case when searching
set smartcase "Unless you put some caps in your search term

"Filetype settings
:filetype plugin on "Turns on plugin support
:filetype indent on "Turns on auto-indenting

"Key mappings
imap jj <Esc>`^ 
